          <div class="prog-event-body">
            <p class="prog-event-category">Workshop with Rose</p>
            <h3>Art of movement with the Feldenkrais method - The back in motion!</h3>
            <p>Do you suffer from neck strain, lower back pain or difficulty bending or turning your head? This workshop is for you! During this morning session, you'll be practising simple, gentle and unusual movements: feeling and developing the rich possibilities of our spinal chain to restore flexibility and vitality to your back. It's an invitation to rediscover a free, lively back and a more fluid everyday life!</p>
            <div class="prog-event-meta">
              <span class="prog-event-price">35 € + 5 € annual membership</span>
              <span class="prog-event-contact"><a href="mailto:rosegiovannini@free.fr">rosegiovannini@free.fr</a> — <a href="http://www.rosegiovannini.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">rosegiovannini.com</a></span>
            </div>
          </div>
        </article>

